read_text = Array[String](["Boss - Get back to work or else I'm not paying you!", "Bob - Party at my house tonight! We're gonna have pizza, soda, and Jenny is gonna be there. ;)", "Wife - I'm going to the store to get groceries. Do you need anything?", "User1426 - I filled out the form, but your company keeps charging me! If this keeps up I'm going to sue!", "Boss - Jill has called in sick and won't be here for the next couple of weeks.", "kid_jensen_11 - hi whats 4*3 my math teacher wont tell me"])
